filing_in_progress

registered

maintaining

retired

8.2 Docket lifecycle states

scheduled

due_soon

overdue

completed

waived

9) Integration tagging (engine routing keys)

Every IPAsset record should carry:

Project (e.g., NS-AEGIS, NS-PG, NS-LUM)

AssetClass

ConfidentialityPosture

ProtectionIntent

Jurisdiction (if applicable)

Routing defaults:

Decisions → GGE

Filing/Docket tasks → quickscope

OSS/license risk flags → NS-AEGIS

Research/prior art threads → DRE

